FRIED CHICKEN

Murdeshwar’s Fried Chicken is a crispy, golden indulgence that delivers bold flavours and satisfying crunch in every bite. Marinated with a secret blend of herbs and traditional spices, the chicken is deep-fried to perfection, creating a juicy, tender interior wrapped in a crunchy, flavorful coating.
Each piece is bursting with the authentic taste of coastal spices, offering a unique twist on the classic fried chicken. Ideal for a hearty meal or a delicious snack, Murdeshwar’s Fried Chicken is comfort food elevated with tradition and care. It’s the ultimate treat for those who crave a rich, spicy, and deeply satisfying fried chicken experience.
